    "1402202": {
        "Desc": "Go to Uther's clothing factory",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Chiori",
                    "T": "Ah, you're here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Chiori! How are the new outfits coming along? Uh, you look kinda tired."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chiori",
                    "T": "Just a few steps left, now. I've handed the rest over to Eloffe. We should be able to make tonight's show."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wow, that's cutting it real close... Are you sure she'll be okay without you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chiori",
                    "T": "Don't worry, I have no intention of giving ground on either front. With the fashion show scheduled for tonight, Uther has closed his factory — this is our only chance to secure any incriminating evidence."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Okay, Paimon totally gets that this is all his fault and he totally deserves it, but wouldn't we technically be trespassing on his property if we just barge in like this?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chiori",
                    "T": "His factory is usually open to the public. It may not be open for business right now, but that doesn't mean visitors can't stop by for a tour."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chiori",
                    "T": "We're just curious customers after all, aren't we?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Well, when you put it that way..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chiori",
                    "T": "Anyway, Uther's factory is right over there. Let's hurry up and get moving."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Uhh... Why would he open a factory over... there?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chiori",
                    "T": "We have different marketing strategies. While I specialize in high-end, custom garments, he prefers low prices and large sales volumes. I dunno... Maybe the rent here is cheap."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Alright... It's really creepy. Paimon would never choose to buy anything from a place like that."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chiori",
                    "T": "You make a good point. Let's all be on our guard."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
