    "1402214": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "This place seems like some kind of warehouse. Blech... And it stinks, too."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh!? What's going on? Our way in's been blocked!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "He wants to trap us in the factory..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chiori",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chiori",
                    "T": "Seems like he knew we'd be coming."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "You did say he knew you really well, didn't you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chiori",
                    "T": "Yes. And that's because... we used to be partners."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "B—But you're practically at each other's throats! Now you're telling us you used to work together!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chiori",
                    "T": "When I first came to Fontaine, we were both fledging designers who longed to gain a foothold in the world of fashion. We shared the same goal, so we decided to work together."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chiori",
                    "T": "In the beginning, we both wanted to make clothes that would stand out from the crowd and shatter tradition — the kind of clothes that would turn heads and leave people in awe."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chiori",
                    "T": "But with every criticism we received, and every sponsor that rejected us... Uther's confidence disappeared little by little."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chiori",
                    "T": "Finally, right before Fashion Week, he came to the conclusion that we wouldn't be able to make the designs we always dreamed of, and we parted ways."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chiori",
                    "T": "For my part, I gambled it all and devoted everything I had to that one week... I came out the other side with something that really made me proud. I was nervous to present it, of course, but I knew it was my chance to show the industry what I was made of. In the end, well..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "You received the acclaim of all Fontaine, while Uther gave up on his dream and turned to making this dodgy stuff?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chiori",
                    "T": "I don't know the exact details of what happened after that. All I know is, after I opened Chioriya Boutique, he's harassed me every year since."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmph! He's just jealous of what you've accomplished. A guy like that doesn't deserve your sympathy."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chiori",
                    "T": "Well, let's focus on getting out of here first."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chiori",
                    "T": "Missing the show is as good as letting him win."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ah, there are some control panels over there! Let's see if any of those buttons do anything!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
